{"tid":2357570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"眼帶狗 沉默了 佢的保單不要收","createTime":"2021-01-07T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T18:03:02.000Z","uid":154406,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0da4ecf22558628fdab0c908bd275917e5a693","tid":2357570,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"眼帶狗 沉默了 佢的保單不要收<br />\n眼帶狗 情動了 但我要J絲打隻手<br />\n<br />\n習慣起底之後誣蔑各位波台狗<br />\n自爆AC怎料還是要出醜數遍<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=eef0bdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n<br />\n我太心廣體胖其實逛街像黎明高調<br />\n各位手足請勿忘掉這位娛樂的大少<br />\n嗯～～～ 嗯～～～<br />\n<br />\nCyrus <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c81be51a53e9c0a0f9bafe6d1e96d44f588f9b","tid":2357570,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"關嗯咩事？"},{"pid":"a231b1eccf3bd0be87ab0e7dbf354e25129b33f0","tid":2357570,"uid":13106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6761b970dee7550f42dabf6aa3a46648398e455","tid":2357570,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c81be51a53e9c0a0f9bafe6d1e96d44f588f9b","tid":2357570,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"關嗯咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"佢係你老友，加唔到你個名入去當比Credit你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58f358f90cd6c90ebd450acbe684ab6270d3821","tid":2357570,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci